Can you provides the use cases for use case for dump file name in "human readable format"?

Already supported two format's used here option, 

('BMC_DUMP_FILENAME_REGEX', type: 'string',
        value: 'BMCDUMP.([a-zA-Z0-9]+).([0-9]+).([0-9]+)',
         description : 'BMC dump file format'
       )
option('SYS_DUMP_FILENAME_REGEX', type: 'string',
         value: 'SYSDUMP.([a-zA-Z0-9]+).([0-9]+).([0-9]+)',
         description : 'System dump file format'
       )
LGTM
idle for long time. Add me back once this is ready for review.
